hildon-desktop (1:2.2.11-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Increase version number of libmatchbox2 build dependency.
  * Hide launcher and switcher if they are shown when a new window is
    mapped. This enables using things like power menu in launcher and
    switcher views.
  * Marc: Changed the default loading screen to a rect created from the theme's
    bg color. Also, remove it after the animation is complete.
  * Adam: Make noise when a window is added to/removed from the switcher,
    effectively, when an application is opened or closed.
  * Adam: Recognize popup menus and such and add/remove from their
    application's thumbnail in the switcher.
  * Thomas: Partial checkin of progress indicator implementation.
  * Jan Arne: Fix pointer grab/ungrab with Home edit menu.
  * Marc: Correct hard-coded menu. Pre-started image viewer.

